  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00567', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '依關稅徵課會計制度之規定，下列敘述何者正確？', '["除辦理關稅徵收之會計業務外，代收相關稅費亦屬其會計業務之實施範圍", "採用權責發生基礎，但過渡時期得先採現金基礎", "會計年度之開始及終了，依會計法規定辦理", "不設置預算控制類科目"]'::jsonb, 0, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 13, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00568', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲機關配合預算執行需要，出納管理人員依規定簽奉機關首長核准設立 100,000 元零用金，作為 零星付款之用，業務執行過程陸續以零用金支付加班費等人事支出12,000元，差旅費30,000元， 講師鐘點費28,000元，試依中央政府普通公務單位會計制度之一致規定，出納管理人員以零用金 支付講師鐘點費時應為之會計分錄為何？', '["借：業務支出 28,000元 ，貸：零用金28,000元", "借：業務支出 28,000元 ，貸：公庫撥入數28,000元", "借：業務支出 28,000元 ，貸：現金28,000元", "不作分錄"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 14, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00569', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '財政部國庫署為調節短期國庫收支，向銀行洽借短期借款，依中央總會計制度、中央政府普通公', '["總 會計", "單位會計", "中央公共債務會計", "附屬單位會計"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 15, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00570', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '依內地稅徵課會計制度之規定，其原始憑證包括下列那些書表？①稅款退還清單  ②應收稅（帳）', '["以前年度應收稅（帳）款月報表", "代收稅款日報表", "無", "僅"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00571', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '甲機關於X05年6月15日購入實驗船1艘1億元，耐用年數40年，預估殘值200萬元。X07年 8月因天災受損無法使用，故於X08年進行修復，修復經費400萬元，X08年10月1日修復完 成並下海航行進行實驗工作，惟修復後只能再使用25年，預估殘值仍為200萬元。X24年2月 28日，甲機關將該實驗船報廢，針對上開交易，甲機關於年度會計報告「決算與會計收支對照表」 的表達或調整，下列何者正確？', '["X05年度歲出決算數及會計支出數均認列折舊", "X08 年度災損修復部分，歲出決算認列「設施及機械設備養護費」，會計不認列支出但應認列 固定資產", "X05年度歲出決算認列「交通運輸及設備」，會計不認列支出但應認列固定資產及當年度折舊", "X24年度歲入決算認列「財產售價收入」，會計無須認列財產交易損失"]'::jsonb, 2, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 17, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00572', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '政府會計觀念公報對於公開報導責任之敘述，何者正確？', '["強調在資源最大可收入的範圍內，重視成本效益分析，採用最適效率及效果的方式提供服務， 以達成施政目標", "政府於達成施政目標過程中，對於資源之籌措及運用，負有公開及忠實表述之責", "確保政府對資源籌措及運用，確實遵循相關法令規定", "為使民眾了解政府資源籌措與運用之過程及結果，除特別預算外，政府總預算案及其法定預算、 決算與總會計報告須予公開報導"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 18, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL),
  ('locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-00573', 'locality-d0d1b9a2', 'locality-d0d1b9a2-moex-110-ac2adf20', 'sub-locality-d0d1b9a2-02', NULL, 'single_choice', '依中央公共債務會計制度之規定，下列主管機關所設置之明細分類帳簿中，應區分債票形式及登', '["庫存債票明細分類帳", "償付公債本金明細分類帳", "償付公債利息明 細分類帳", "公債明細分類帳"]'::jsonb, 1, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T12:34:10+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "2f24e4c86924", "answer_pdf_sha1": "b01c6334ecca", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "110190", "c": "313", "s": "1507", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "政府會計", "year": "110", "exam_name": "110年特種考試地方政府公務人員考試", "original_question_number": 19, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "civil_slug": "locality", "civil_category": "會計"}'::jsonb, NULL)
